---
/*
  VOICE REFERENCES:
  
  PROPHET: "The signs are here. YAHUSHA returns. Watch and be ready."
  OG MENTOR: "Watch the signs. Work the harvest. Endure to the end. That's the assignment."
  HOOD PHILOSOPHER: "The world sleeps. The remnant wakes. Don't get caught sleeping."
  ENTREPRENEUR: "Time is your most limited resource. Spend it on eternity."
  
  SACRED NAMES: YAHUAH, YAHUSHA, RUACH HAQODESH, EL ELYON
*/
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="End-Times">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 md:py-16 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-amber-100">End-Times</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p class="lead text-xl text-neutral-300">
        We are living in the last days. The signs are all around us. The question is: are you ready for the return of YAHUSHA HAMASHIACH?
      </p>

      <h2>Watch & Work</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-4">
        YAHUSHA told us to watch and work until He returns. Here's your checklist:
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-4 not-prose">
        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="text-amber-500 text-3xl font-bold flex-shrink-0">1</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-amber-100 font-bold text-lg mb-2">Watch the Signs</h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-400">
                Wars, earthquakes, false prophets, persecution, the gospel preached to all nations. 
                Stay alert. Discern the times. Don't be caught sleeping.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="text-amber-500 text-3xl font-bold flex-shrink-0">2</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-amber-100 font-bold text-lg mb-2">Work the Harvest</h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-400">
                The fields are white. The laborers are few. Share the Gospel. Make disciples. 
                Time is short—every soul matters.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="text-amber-500 text-3xl font-bold flex-shrink-0">3</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-amber-100 font-bold text-lg mb-2">Endure to the End</h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-400">
                Persecution will come. Trials will increase. But he who endures to the end will be saved (Matthew 24:13). 
                Hold fast to your faith—no matter the cost.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>The Signs of the Times</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-300">
        YAHUSHA warned us to watch. We see the signs unfolding:
      </p>

      <ul class="text-neutral-300 space-y-2">
        <li>Wars and rumors of wars (Matthew 24:6)</li>
        <li>Earthquakes in various places (Matthew 24:7)</li>
        <li>False prophets deceiving many (Matthew 24:11)</li>
        <li>The love of many growing cold (Matthew 24:12)</li>
        <li>The gospel preached to all nations (Matthew 24:14)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>The Tribulation</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-300">
        A time of great tribulation is coming—a time of trouble such as the world has never seen (Matthew 24:21). 
        But those who call on the Name of YAHUAH will be saved. Those who endure will reign with Him.
      </p>

      <h2>The Return of Mashiach</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-300">
        YAHUSHA is coming back. Not as a suffering servant, but as a conquering King. 
        Every eye will see Him (Revelation 1:7). The trumpet will sound. The dead in Mashiach will rise. 
        The remnant will be gathered.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-amber-900/20 border border-amber-800/50 rounded-lg p-6 my-8">
        <p class="text-amber-100 font-semibold mb-2">Are you ready?</p>
        <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-0">
          Repent. Turn from sin. Walk in holiness. Watch. Work. Endure. 
          The hour is late, but the promise is sure: YAHUSHA HAMASHIACH is coming back.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Prepare for His Return -->
      <div class="mt-12 bg-neutral-950 border border-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-100 mb-6 text-center">Prepare for His Return</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <a href="/feasts" class="group block p-6 bg-neutral-900 rounded-lg border border-neutral-800 hover:border-amber-700 transition-colors">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-100 group-hover:text-amber-200 mb-2">Feasts of YAH</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Understand the prophetic timeline through the Feasts</p>
          </a>
          
          <a href="/spiritual-warfare" class="group block p-6 bg-neutral-900 rounded-lg border border-neutral-800 hover:border-amber-700 transition-colors">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-100 group-hover:text-amber-200 mb-2">Spiritual Warfare</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Put on the armor and prepare for the final battle</p>
          </a>
          
          <a href="/identity-and-messiah" class="group block p-6 bg-neutral-900 rounded-lg border border-neutral-800 hover:border-amber-700 transition-colors">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-100 group-hover:text-amber-200 mb-2">Identity & Mashiach</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Know who you are in YAHUSHA HAMASHIACH</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
